thanks!</comment>
                    <comment id="12609902" author="rpuch" created="Wed, 2 Jul 2008 13:41:15 +0100"  >I&amp;#39;m not sure is it correct to reopen the issue, but it turned out that the supplied patch breaks class unloading in some cases. I&amp;#39;m going to attach a patch which stops the reaper thread too, so no problems arise because of it.</comment>
                    <comment id="12609903" author="rpuch" created="Wed, 2 Jul 2008 13:42:22 +0100"  >This patch stops the ReaperThread on shutdown too.</comment>
